    "updated_at": "2015-08-31T10:56:35Z",
    "body": "It would be interesting/fun to write a cross-platform app store in Electron, then use it to promote electron apps. (Which would not need to bundle the electron runtime due to the presence of it in the app store itself.)\n\nExtra points for basing it on npm or a fork of it. (Such as apm.)\n\nThere's a partial list of electron apps and tools here: https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome-electron\n"
  },
