    "updated_at": "2015-08-31T16:44:26Z",
    "body": "@Tribex thanks for sharing that list. pretty cool.\n\nI have been thinking that I might just have to build a store as well since there is really nothing I have been able to find. [Gum Road](https://gumroad.com/) is a nice site to handle sales, but it's not a store, and you can't search it. So you still have to find ways to get your app in front of as many people as possible.\n\nThe nice thing about a store is that the people there are already looking for an app, so it increases your chance of getting installs being it free or paid.\n"
