    "created_at": "2015-09-01T00:37:30Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-01T00:37:30Z",
    "body": "Distributing a store will be easier than distributing an app I believe. The demographic for distributing a single app is limited to that apps functionality.\n\nWhile a store on the other hand has the benefit of containing many apps thus creating a much larger demographic that may be interested.\n\nie. you might not be interested in buying an oven mit, but you might be interested in buying something from a store that also sells oven mits.\n"
  },
