    "updated_at": "2015-09-01T02:27:05Z",
    "body": "Promoting electron apps is the same with promoting apps written with other frameworks, different platforms have their own way of promoting apps. On OS X there is app store, on Windows there are various third party app markets, and for games you can submit to Steam store.\n\nIn future we may have our own app store when #673 is done, but it will be years later.\n"
